{"tid":1741361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急求推]11月24區議會選舉-票戰","createTime":"2019-11-20T10:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T14:09:08.000Z","uid":144435,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ca9147aa98a1568598b28d77eb8cdadf28792d70","tid":1741361,"uid":144435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:00:03.000Z","msg":"可能呢個post好快沉底<br />\n但我希望見到呢個post嘅人都可以幫手推一推<br />\n.<br />\n事緣11月24係區議會選舉<br />\n小弟成家人都有票係手<br />\n但由於老竇老母都係廢老藍絲<br />\n再加上近呢幾屆啲建制派班區議員都有科少少水比投佢票嘅人<br />\n(老母對上一次收咗300蚊)<br />\n所以小弟諗到一個既能孝順父母<br />\n又能令到父母投票比民主黨議員<br />\n就係收賣自己老竇老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n.<br />\n我提議各位連登巴打絲打<br />\n每人用$1000去屋企樓下就近嘅超級市場換成禮券<br />\n然後同老竇老母講只要投民主派嘅區議員一票<br />\n就會得到$500嘅超級市場禮券<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之科得多過建制派議員少少就okay<br />\n成件事 淨係同自己老竇老母講 唔對外傳<br />\n同佢哋講傳開要坐監 犯賄賂條例 <br />\n老竇老母驚死 一定唔會爆響口 <br />\n跟手就咁每人幫民主派賺兩票 慢慢就可以積少成多<br />\n到時你又開心 父母又開心 雙贏局面咪幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加上仔女孝敬老竇老母 天經地義喎<br />\n.<br />\n希望到時民主派議員當選 <br />\n我哋再由區議會開始做起 <br />\n務求未來上至立法會 下至區議會議員都係民主派<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港人加油！<br />\n血債票償</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\nP.S:頭先搵老母試咗一下 <br />\n話十一月投民主派議員會派500蚊超市禮券<br />\n佢都已經即刻話投俾民主派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5231b3ef388687af01bc1e65169cefa39a6ae438","tid":1741361,"uid":144435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:00:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b175d7505b285d6b7ce162ff0b91d02ba2b01c79","tid":1741361,"uid":144435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:00:35.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"f703ddca7b9c8e869f2abb8d2c9a11d98479ba8b","tid":1741361,"uid":144435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:00:46.000Z","msg":"推3/10"},{"pid":"f6f88de608bd7d20319539cb7b907ff870318d6c","tid":1741361,"uid":35604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:00:50.000Z","msg":"刪左句血債票償佢啦"},{"pid":"bd08de27d8a66d9c866aa4302fb5bee3a70bf825","tid":1741361,"uid":144435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:00:58.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"5e5b4590aae341fdc9374c15419190c10a75b758","tid":1741361,"uid":144435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:01:43.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"aba8bf0e04c221d7f2556acee8412f3614f52c91","tid":1741361,"uid":144435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:01:53.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"ddec0484c4e6e83f05f924cd49750b72d8d20b22","tid":1741361,"uid":144435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:02:03.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"512fa08172e04abef8cac57dc5a8a43e06329de7","tid":1741361,"uid":144435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:02:13.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"d1c1c146635b078817470b11fd7f7ad76a031688","tid":1741361,"uid":144435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:02:23.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"c33fc0134cfa43bdbbb2131636a7bb61da0b143b","tid":1741361,"uid":144435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:02:33.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"7e9fc17211224e2fed4bb52387a992c6f75ec6b4","tid":1741361,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:02:34.000Z","msg":"如果知兩老會投比垃圾，就諗下計洗走佢地，唔比佢地去投票好過"},{"pid":"776541a0a327bcf674619cdea37ada6a9e5c0aed","tid":1741361,"uid":144435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e9fc17211224e2fed4bb52387a992c6f75ec6b4","tid":1741361,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:02:34.000Z","msg":"如果知兩老會投比垃圾，就諗下計洗走佢地，唔比佢地去投票好過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:03:05.000Z","msg":"可以考慮趁佢地沖涼收鳩佢地身份證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ed01c4bf